page.title: 03Prestwood Schoolday - Cont.
page.content: "Yuc!". After that we had English and then first play (10.40 - 11.00). After that we had half an hour of French after finishing off our English. After that we had our lunch break. I had a cello lesson till half past twelve. Then I went and had lunch. After that I played ball-semi with Emma until the bell went at 13.25. Then we had Geography and Art until the bell went for last break at 14.40. After that we had a tables and spelling test until the final bell went at 15.45. I got my bag and coat and walked home with Sarah and waited for my mum. When I got in I watched Children's ITV television and had a cup of tea. Then I got changed for modern and tap-dancing. I am at Grade 3 Modern and Grade 2 Tap. I shall soon take Grade 2 exam. After that I came home and had my tea - sausages and chips. Cont.....
